On Error Resume Next 

Dim objApp
Dim objIE
Dim objWindow

Set objApp = CreateObject("Shell.Application")
Set objIE = Nothing

For Each objWindow In objApp.Windows
  If (InStr(objWindow.Name, "Internet Explorer")) Then
    Set objIE = objWindow
    Exit For
  End If
Next

objIE.Navigate(WScript.Arguments(0))

objApp = Nothing 
objIE = Nothing 
objWindow = Nothing
